Name: django-sysinfo
Version: 0.3
Summary: Simple django app to expose system infos: libraries version, databae server infos...
Home-page: https://github.com/saxix/django-sysinfo
Author: Stefano Apostolico
Author-email: s.apostolico@gmail.com
